{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d0cd5a164a","title":"中央关于谭震林等任职和军队整编问题给陈毅的复电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b1cfd2c1d8","index":0,"year":1952,"month":6,"day":9,"articleId":"d0cd5a164a"}],"tags":[{"id":"1feb996ca7","name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"id":"89f0012853","name":"谭震林","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8cac28713b","type":"title","text":"中央关于谭震林等任职和军队整编问题给陈毅的复电","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d0cd5a164a"},{"id":"b35c28a292","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d0cd5a164a"},{"id":"4c2a7a95ed","type":"appellation","text":"陈毅同志，并华东局，上海市委：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d0cd5a164a"},{"id":"c7edb9869b","type":"paragraph","text":"六月八日来电收到。同意你的各项意见。谭震林同志任华东军政委员会副主席，在饶治病期间代行主席职权，待提交中央人民政府任命后即可就职。同意上海市府党组书记仍由潘汉年同志担任，方毅同志改任副书记。同意上海市总工会党组书记仍由刘长胜同志担任，钟民同志改任副书记。军队整编转业应加紧督促，达到“转业给饭吃、走向生产”之目的，防止用大批裁员的办法，这些意见是正确的。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d0cd5a164a"},{"id":"88beb24838","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央六月九日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d0cd5a164a"}],"page":{"id":"37676cc04c","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d0cd5a164a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}